{"id":248264,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/global-voices-乌克兰：舍甫琴科转战政坛/","date":"2012-08-22T02:30:10Z","modified":"2012-08-22T02:30:10Z","title":"Global Voices | 乌克兰：舍甫琴科转战政坛","content":"<p><p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ukrainian_parliamentary_election,_2012\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ukrainian_parliamentary_election,_2012\">十月廿八日乌克兰国会大选</a>整三个月前的七月廿八日，足球明星<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andriy_Shevchenko\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andriy_Shevchenko\">安德列．舍甫琴科</a>宣布他将退出球坛<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-19099565\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-19099565\">进军政坛</a>。</p>\n<p>许多乌克兰球迷相当失望，而这已经是委婉的形容。倒不是因为他决定从政：毕竟名人为各方政治势力背书或是参与政治已习以为常，乌克兰也没什么人还认为他们是为公众利益着想。舍甫琴科的问题在于他选择在下次选举中代表的政党。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/neeka/\" title=\"文章导读 Veronica Khokhlova\">Veronica Khokhlova</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/hllee/\" title=\"文章导读 Hsu-Lei Lee\">Hsu-Lei Lee</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/08/06/ukraine-andriy-shevchenko-retires-from-football-enters-politics/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2012/08/22/11379/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><br />分享: <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hemidemi.com/user_bookmark/new?title=%E4%B9%8C%E5%85%8B%E5%85%B0%EF%BC%9A%E8%88%8D%E7%94%AB%E7%90%B4%E7%A7%91%E8%BD%AC%E6%88%98%E6%94%BF%E5%9D%9B&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F22%2F11379%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F22%2F11379%2F&#03